sellerCard.description:
I am Mike,  a full-stack developer with more than 4 years of experience in both designing and development of web applications using these technologies: ReactJS, NodeJS, WEB3, NextJS, ReactJS, Elixir / Phoenix.

Let's get your project moving! I am extremely detail-oriented and have a passion for web design and development. It's is my personal goal to ensure that everyone who does business with me gets VIP treatment and exceptional quality.

description.content:
As a professional Squarespace web designer, I will create a responsive website tailored to your needs. With 6 years of experience, I specialize in delivering visually stunning and user-friendly designs that drive results.


About This Gig:

With my expertise in Squarespace, I will design or redesign your squarespace website to align with your brand identity and goals. Whether you're starting from scratch or need a revamp, I've got you covered.


Why Choose Me?

By selecting my services, you'll benefit from my years of experience in squarespace, attention to detail, and dedication to client satisfaction. I take the time to understand your unique requirements and tailor the design to meet your specific needs.


By ordering my Gig, you'll receive a unique website that enhances your online presence. Take your business to new heights today!


  • Professional Squarespace web design
  • Responsive and user-friendly layouts
  • Prompt communication and attentive service
  • Customized squarespace design to enhance your brand
  • Attention to detail and high-quality work


Don't miss out on this opportunity to elevate your online presence. Place your order now and let's create an impactful website together!

questionsAndAnswers.question: What details do you need to start the website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
I need following things from you to start the project:

1. Squarespace login details
2. Logo and branding colors
3. Page names for website
4. Content for pages
5. Reference websites you like
